{"tid":1470363,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢兩個幾月嚟一啲關於operation上嘅建議","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:55:43.000Z","uid":209526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"241fda6a0af809cc06c5d3799987ab135dd76c0c","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「和理非唔好太潔癖 勇武唔好太腦充血」</span></strong></strong>大家多啲溝通，無大台係難㗎啦，但係雙方唔好咁極端，即使覺得有唔合理嘅地方，唔好淨係屌或者ban（例如唔好扔低一句說話就草率了結）嘗試心平氣和，提出各自嘅建議同埋目的，等大家明白你/你組人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 現場根據<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「語氣」「資訊準確性」「建議行動」</span></strong></span>呢三大原則發怖消息。<br />\n理解現場好多時情況一緊張會好難控制語氣，各位手足盡量留意翻語氣！ 盡量準確/fact check資訊再以簡潔清晰咁發怖！<br />\n（例如：「圍緊假公安，有手足暈左，大家唔好再哄埋黎。」<br />\n當時「假公安」唔係準確資訊<br />\n亦唔係佢需要傳遞嘅訊息 有手足暈左需要大家散開先至係<br />\n而「假公安」呢樣嘢就偏偏只會令更多聽到嘅人哄埋去睇熱鬧<br />\n所以，前因後果如果唔係你最需要傳達嘅訊息 就有需要先後補）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 實地認證哨兵隊未成形 但唔好因為網絡擠塞而令自己完全無法接收資訊 前線專注攻防唔會睇電話好合理 後排嘅都要走吓位唔好死坐 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">確保資訊接收同傳遞俾前線</span></span></strong> 當然要記得上面講嘅 語氣、資訊、建議行動 3大原則<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 捉鬼敢死隊要有自制能力 成功識破而制服後 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>急call記者大踢爆</strong></span> 然後放人 唔好死圍浪費人力同時間"},{"pid":"429029ec239e1cff80df68ce99642b4f8a76d971","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6ecd6f20f4292452b12a5d782e6b735d3f6c898a","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ce0a79b34ad22ee9fe8c0747f0bc1c21323f6594","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a1963ff3b16dc5855ec959fb19a81f352e83abec","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c838705536d4f7fede329c7220d9f03b13af86cc","tid":1470363,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"cb3c766d4cbbaa421c3309d6b402951f87129660","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"05f8297c1d8e81f65ecabab00ba5cd7c656f9f54","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"42b6dc8a2e493109051e00ec69a6016f47c9ac11","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"795be6d5c4c54b74beace2bf2272ee0b2d524d7e","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"187908106005ceafb4fa1f3ac5e56b1bc3a73910","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"fa29249839417faa1b3d490081042072833b32c1","tid":1470363,"uid":209526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"479953832134fcf85fb920be0a656e0b40048329","tid":1470363,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59bf48b3ebc42a03ed8b99052525f26141ee7288","tid":1470363,"uid":130450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}